@OpeeFornenom:  
Even better, cast [Conquer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Conquer) and follow-up by *casting* [Foreshadow](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Foreshadow)!   

The card itself is mediocre at best though..sure there are (potentially) really good lands to steal, but if I was running a land destruction deck, i'd be destroying opponents lands, not taking them. Also in a LD deck, [Plow Under](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plow Under) fits the bill much better. Although you probably won't have any friends to play against after a couple of resolved Plow Under spells..and with good reason, that card is full of hatred.

